text: Hrvoje Telišman (born 25 December 1972) is a Croatian rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Croatia Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zagreb
